DOC.brief_summary: This study is being conducted to assess mechanistic blood biomarkers of CAT-1004 in healthy humans.
DOC.brief_title: A Study of CAT-1004 Biomarkers in Healthy Subjects
DOC.criteria: Good health as determined by medical history, vital signs, EGC, physical exam and clinical lab results BMI between 18 and 30 kg/m2 inclusive Viral or bacterial infection within 21 days prior to randomization Use of prescription drugs, nonprescription drugs, herbals and dietary supplements within 7 days prior to randomization
